		<title>Phara, Queen of NinjaVideo, Pleads Guilty To Conspiracy and Copyright Infringement</title>
		<link>http://feed.torrentfreak.com/~r/Torrentfreak/~3/XG1raGvlix8/</link>
		<comments>http://torrentfreak.com/phara-queen-of-ninjavideo-pleads-guilty-to-conspiracy-and-copyright-infringement-110930/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 30 Sep 2011 19:20:47 +0000</pubDate>
