		<title>Vuze Brings BitTorrent to Your TV, and Thousands of Other Devices</title>
		<link>http://feed.torrentfreak.com/~r/Torrentfreak/~3/QNIRcoU6H8o/</link>
		<comments>http://torrentfreak.com/vuze-brings-bittorrent-to-your-tv-and-thousands-of-other-devices-110925/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 25 Sep 2011 20:32:49 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Ernesto</dc:creator>
