		<title>NinjaVideo Founder Faces Jail Time Following Guilty Plea</title>
		<link>http://feed.torrentfreak.com/~r/Torrentfreak/~3/cK_Xv1EFrIs/</link>
		<comments>http://torrentfreak.com/ninjavideo-founder-faces-jail-time-following-guilty-plea-110924/#comments</comments>
