		<title>uTorrent Adds Android, iOS, PS3 and Xbox Integration</title>
		<link>http://feed.torrentfreak.com/~r/Torrentfreak/~3/SUx4NBddzF4/</link>
		<comments>http://torrentfreak.com/utorrent-adds-android-ios-ps3-and-xbox-integration-110922/#comments</comments>
